      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">Portrait photograph. Novaković in a dark jacket, white shirt and dark necktie with pale stripes. His has thinning hair and a moustache.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">Novaković established socialist Yugoslavia’s first public film production company, ‘Zvezda’, in 1945. He was a film director, film historian and longstanding professor of theatre, film and radio at the Faculty of Dramatic Arts in Belgrade.</ab>
